headline: Gartner Identifies Top Three Priorities for CMOs to Deliver Marketing Excellence in 2025
summary: STAMFORD, Conn., December 03, 2024--With increased pressure to deliver growth and support cross-functional work, Gartner, Inc. has identified three priorities for CMOs to deliver marketing excellence in 2025.
